    <div class="container">
      <h2><img src="/images/icons/rewards.svg"></img></h2>
      <h3>Welcome! Refer-a-friend &amp; get rewarded.</h3>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="one-half column">
          <p>Share your unique link and we'll give you an <b>extra £5</b> (on top of the £10 we'll already give you) when you sign-up a friend.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="one-half column">
